response.overview: A UFO comes to earth in search of Honey, Bunny, Zordar and Popat. Honey, Bunny, Zordar and Popat go to the space center. Bunny mistakenly activates a rocket. All four of them hide in the UFO but the UFO leaves with them. The "Maharaj" gives all four of them a task. All of them get lost in space. Zordar, Honey, Bunny and Popat go to the other planet.
response.title: Honey Bunny Lost In Space
